metadata.name: Very Blue Dream
metadata.description:
Special technique I am using for creating this piece called neurographics. Three circles of flower represent Trust, Sexuality and Love. Leaves show growth from one phase to another, blessed with powers of neuro lines. I believe this painting will help you achieve your dream love life. After purchase it is advisable to make 3 step psychological exercise to help your brain collect your own code from the lines.

Hard copy may be send to collector. PDF,JPEG,PNG formats are available as well.
